resources.string: Hide your private photos and videos into privacy gallery
The selected file will be invisible to others. Are you sure you want to do this?
Once the selected file is unhide, it will be visible to others. Are you sure you want to do this?
After the selected file is deleted, it will not be recovered. Are you sure you want to delete it?
You must create a password to protect your private files.
1. What happens if I delete the files in the privacy gallery?
If you click the delete button, the selected photo or video will be permanently deleted, please be sure to confirm it carefully before deleting.
The Privacy Gallery does not automatically delete files unless you click Unhide or Delete.
If you uninstall the app, you need to download this app again before you can restore the files in the privacy gallery to the original location, so please confirm before uninstalling.
2. Will the files be placed in the privacy gallery disappear?
3. If the application is uninstalled, can the file in the privacy gallery be retrieved?
Do not uninstall Fast Cleaner before the photos and videos in gallery vault have not been unhidden!
Deleting files in the gallery vault is permanent, so please be sure to confirm carefully before deleting it.
